'''Skrilling''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Skrilling/Legends|Skrilling]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Agriworld-2079/Legends|Agriworld-2079]]. Most Skrillings were fluent in both Skrilling language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they spoke Basic with a nasal quality due to their breathing tubes, which gave them a whining accent.

They were only literate in their own language.

